{"tid":1567440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果被敵人稱讚，你可能做錯了些甚麼","createTime":"2019-09-14T05:32:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T06:00:25.000Z","uid":245820,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2aa1d9a1a453b8cef1a159180641c66e218e16d6","tid":1567440,"uid":245820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:32:53.000Z","msg":"唔係話唔俾唱，但係時候做下其他嘢啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1480507-20190914.htm?spTabChangeable=0&amp;fbclid=IwAR1m1a6uQS7Oy-IeeDb8IReOWPMWx9iwA1ztaOM_8Jp5VYtk3CVcgdTTbO8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1480507-20190914.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0%26fbclid%3DIwAR1m1a6uQS7Oy-IeeDb8IReOWPMWx9iwA1ztaOM_8Jp5VYtk3CVcgdTTbO8&d=CilPfclB3esq2vqCdqPDZ8dEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=eb9f40c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1480507-20190914.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0%26fbclid%3DIwAR1m1a6uQS7Oy-IeeDb8IReOWPMWx9iwA1ztaOM_8Jp5VYtk3CVcgdTTbO8&h=ee37c13e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1480507-20190914.htm?spTabChangeable=0&amp;fbclid=IwAR1m1a6uQS7Oy-IeeDb8IReOWPMWx9iwA1ztaOM_8Jp5VYtk3CVcgdTTbO8</a><br />\n<br />\n曾鈺成讚《願榮光歸香港》高質　反映文宣水平相當高<br />\n<br />\n近日在多個場合都有大批市民齊唱反修例歌曲《願榮光歸香港》，立法會前主席曾鈺成表示，這首歌他有聽過，被問到歌詞是否有港獨意味，他表示不想評論歌曲的含意，讚揚歌曲的技巧和質素相當高，相信是出自專業人士之手。他又表示，特首林鄭月娥在公開與非公開場合都曾承認，在文宣工作方面，政府遠遠落後於反對的一方，由這首歌曲已充分反映反對一方的文宣水平相當高。<br />\n<br />\n被問到政府是否需要仿傚，亦要作曲做文宣，曾鈺成估計，政府亦正在思考。<br />\n<br />\n對於近日當大批市民到各區唱此歌時，曾與唱國歌的人士發生衝突，曾鈺成表示，如果唱歌作為和平表達意見和情緒表達的方式，是無可厚非，如果同場有政見不同的人士，互相都是以和平方式表達立場，希望各方都能保特克制，不要令和平表達演變為暴力衝突。"},{"pid":"1e06749986fe4d0a956c788eda4e35da61c0426e","tid":1567440,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:34:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日見</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i6v9Jdp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi6v9Jdp.jpg&h=6cbe719f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cJFtYML.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcJFtYML.jpg&h=a79b44b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cbc130dffdf99c4c46e515a8c2cd24420945d393","tid":1567440,"uid":245820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:58:43.000Z","msg":"915"},{"pid":"432ac64bc3f25193196996ce23654d69356fc8a1","tid":1567440,"uid":245820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:58:53.000Z","msg":"915"},{"pid":"caf7ce7ab432ee01baa6a5cbd0f43247ab63b378","tid":1567440,"uid":245820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:59:05.000Z","msg":"915"},{"pid":"ef8fdb83ff754516d9f44f75bb673e393793336b","tid":1567440,"uid":245820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:59:18.000Z","msg":"915"},{"pid":"0e2a2cfb87ee15f1f640285ef7cfd90a5b9f3a29","tid":1567440,"uid":245820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:59:29.000Z","msg":"915"},{"pid":"c2655aac1b59851f1916a7e12602e31f9125cce3","tid":1567440,"uid":245820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:59:40.000Z","msg":"915"},{"pid":"e7fb62105fe829e2fbea60276f2da972187616de","tid":1567440,"uid":245820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:59:53.000Z","msg":"915"},{"pid":"87f0851820483ea9f31640ea79e2259ab02f8ca3","tid":1567440,"uid":245820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:00:03.000Z","msg":"915"},{"pid":"589100d41f464394ceebe2832c68681403787f97","tid":1567440,"uid":245820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:00:15.000Z","msg":"915"},{"pid":"e58ae5cfd8ca7dc4c02aa5f59d171d0c8613aba1","tid":1567440,"uid":245820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:00:25.000Z","msg":"915"}]}